- Fix common OCR/wording issues: normalize "increment" → "increase"; correct plural/singular inconsistencies.

Final note
All suggested changes stay within the fixed canonical schema (use only CAUSES, INCREASES, DECREASES, etc.). Applying these normalization and relation-selection rules will improve precision, reduce duplicate/ambiguous argument forms, and yield higher-quality, more comparable triplets for evaluation.
